# RPi archive on the running Pi (for kernel updates). Trusted: yes for the same
# reason as the build-time copy in mkosi.sandbox/: trixie's sqv rejects the RPi
# key's SHA1 binding signature (policy change 2026-02-01). Revisit if RPi re-keys.
Types: deb
URIs: http://archive.raspberrypi.com/debian/
Suites: trixie
Components: main
Trusted: yes
